{"id": "art-1431", "label": "Art. 1431", "title": "Art. 1431", "slug": "art-1431", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1208901409\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2198\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1208901409\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 143<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1325734234\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2197\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1325734234\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Directorii sunt responsabili cu luarea tuturor\nm&#259;surilor aferente conducerii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nîn limitele obiectului de activitate al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu respectarea <span class=SpellE>competen&#355;elor</span>\nexclusive rezervate de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> sau de\nactul constitutiv consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1674618942\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1674618942\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Modul de organizare a <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndirectorilor poate fi stabilit prin actul constitutiv sau prin decizie a\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_48473952\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_48473952\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Orice administrator poate solicita directorilor <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> cu privire la conducerea operativ&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. Directorii vor informa consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, în mod regulat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncuprinz&#259;tor, asupra <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span>\nîntreprinse <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> asupra celor avute în vedere.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_618426832\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2194\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_618426832\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Directorii pot fi <span class=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span>\noricând de c&#259;tre consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.\nÎn cazul în care revocarea survine f&#259;r&#259; just&#259; cauz&#259;,\ndirectorul în cauz&#259; este <span class=SpellE>îndrept&#259;&#355;it</span>\nla plata unor daune-interese.</span></p>"}